     Chemistry has several job types available, but the main employment opportunities are in the private sector, and pharmacology and parasitology chemists are in high demand.
 Employment opportunities right now are with the following companies:
*University of Georgia - Organic Chemistry Co-TA
*Noramco - R&D Technician
*Noramco - Analytical Scientist
*Noramco - Process Scientist
*Piedmont Healthcare - Medical Technologist
